403
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:46,790
Father! Father!

404
00:36:46,790 --> 00:36:49,620
Xun'er. Xun'er.

405
00:36:49,620 --> 00:36:53,730
We don't want you to go
but this is Dragon Mother's order.

406
00:36:53,730 --> 00:36:57,010
I don't want to go to the Xiao family!

407
00:36:57,010 --> 00:37:00,010
Xun'er, be good.

408
00:37:00,010 --> 00:37:02,920
I will come to see you every year, all right?

409
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:05,620
